{"tid":918362,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Red Dead Redemption 2》開放線上多人遊戲模式","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T19:08:32.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"13809f523bb64413399c9d3cfcb7745f83054011","tid":918362,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"被稱為有着「西部版 GTA」的《Red Dead Redemption 2》，推出後引起熱烈反應，大家都幾乎廢寢忘餐的沉迷在遊戲世界中。而各位期待已久的線上多人遊戲模式亦終於得到官方確認，將於本月正式登場。Rockstar 宣佈《Red Dead Redemption 2》的在線多人遊戲模式 Red Dead Online 會於美國時間 11 月 27 日早上 8 時 30 分以測試形式推出，其後再陸續開放更多玩家參與，到 11 月 30 日將會完全開放，以有趣的新方式演化故事，玩家可以更改角色能力，並最多可 8 人同時連線進行任務，甚至是日後團戰。有關《Red Dead Redemption 2》 線上多人遊戲模式將適用於 PlayStation 4 及 Xbox One 用家，各位不妨多加留意着。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bqp9jcqlXXj/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBqp9jcqlXXj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b13d3e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBqp9jcqlXXj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=40a36a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bqp9jcqlXXj/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n轉自 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/11/red-dead-redemption-2-online-beta-program\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F11%2Fred-dead-redemption-2-online-beta-program&d=do1kgsn4wvWs8BeP3lr9iDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ecfa7f32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/11/red-dead-redemption-2-online-beta-program</a>"},{"pid":"d05bfd22258c427dc1b340b98786aee005a1048a","tid":918362,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a